sequenceDiagram
    participant vLLM as vLLM Pod<br/>ZMQ PUB 5557/TCP
    participant ZMQ as ZMQ Subscriber<br/>5557/TCP
    participant Pool as KV-Events Pool<br/>(Sharded Workers)
    participant Adapter as Engine Adapter<br/>(vLLM/SGLang)
    participant Index as Block Index<br/>(InMemory/Redis)
    participant EPP as Inference Scheduler<br/>(EPP)
    participant Indexer as KV-Cache Indexer
    participant TokenProc as Token Processor
    participant Scorer as KVBlock Scorer
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Tokenizer as UDS Tokenizer<br/>Unix Socket gRPC
    participant GPU as GPU Memory
    participant Staging as CPU Staging Buffer
    participant Storage as Shared Storage<br/>(PVC / S3)

    Note over vLLM, Index: Flow 1: KV-Event Ingestion (Write Path)
    vLLM->>ZMQ: BlockStored / BlockRemoved / AllBlocksCleared<br/>ZMQ PUB/SUB 5557/TCP, No Auth
    ZMQ->>Pool: Route by FNV-1a(pod_id)<br/>Go channels (in-process)
    Pool->>Adapter: Parse engine-specific event<br/>Function call
    Pool->>Index: Update block index<br/>Function call or Redis 6379/TCP

    Note over EPP, Scorer: Flow 2: Pod Scoring (Read Path)
    EPP->>Indexer: ScoreTokens(prompt, model)<br/>Function call (library embed)
    Indexer->>TokenProc: Hash prompt tokens<br/>Function call
    Indexer->>Index: Lookup matching blocks<br/>Function call or Redis 6379/TCP
    Indexer->>Scorer: Compute per-pod scores<br/>Function call
    Scorer-->>Indexer: Scored pod list
    Indexer-->>EPP: Pod scores (sorted)

    Note over GPU, Storage: Flow 3: KV-Cache Offloading (FS Backend)
    GPU->>Staging: CUDA memcpy (async)<br/>In-process
    Staging->>Storage: Write KV blocks<br/>POSIX I/O or HTTPS/443 (S3)<br/>No Auth or AWS IAM

    Note over K8s, ZMQ: Flow 4: Pod Auto-Discovery
    K8s-->>Pool: Pod watch events<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    Pool->>ZMQ: Create/remove subscriber<br/>per discovered pod
    ZMQ->>vLLM: ZMQ CONNECT 5557/TCP

    Note over Tokenizer, HF: Flow 5: Tokenizer Model Loading
    Tokenizer->>HF: Download tokenizer<br/>HTTPS/443, HF_TOKEN Bearer
    HF-->>Tokenizer: Tokenizer model files
    Indexer->>Tokenizer: Tokenize prompt<br/>gRPC via Unix Domain Socket
    Tokenizer-->>Indexer: Token IDs
